6ad?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77c6935805de248e013f0facec9f16ad?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77c6935805de248e013f0facec9f16ad?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1704840758, "last_modified": 1704840893}, "last_reply_by": "baizhu", "last_touched": 1709868327, "title": "[求推荐] 你们都用什么擦屏幕？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1021409", "created": 1709786781, "deleted": 0, "content": "买过各种布，棉的，绒的，织物的，擦汽车的，擦眼镜的，但没买过官方的那个。\r\n买过各种清洁剂，喷雾的，啫喱的，甚至还用过洗板的 530 。\r\n但每次擦都有水印，油印，擦不干净，看着别扭的很。", "content_rendered": "买过各种布，棉的，绒的，织物的，擦汽车的，擦眼镜的，但没买过官方的那个。<br />买过各种清洁剂，喷雾的，啫喱的，甚至还用过洗板的 530 。<br />但每次擦都有水印，油印，擦不干净，看着别扭的很。", "last_modified": 1709786781, "replies": 93, "id": 1021409}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/41ae/36ec/417_large.png?m=1625409262", "name": "software", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/41ae/36ec/417_normal.png?m=1625409262", "title": "软件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/software", "topics": 737, "footer": "", "header": "关于软件使用的日常讨论", "title_alternative": "Software", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/41ae/36ec/417_mini.png?m=1625409262", "stars": 313, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 417, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 668606, "username": "Int100", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Int100", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08ea/047d/668606_mini.png?m=1704113819", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08ea/047d/668606_normal.png?m=1704113819", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08ea/047d/668606_large.png?m=1704113819", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08ea/047d/668606_xlarge.png?m=1704113819", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08ea/047d/668606_xlarge.png?m=1704113819", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08ea/047d/668606_xlarge.png?m=1704113819", "created": 1703587756, "last_modified": 1704113819}, "last_reply_by": "rockxsj", "last_touched": 1709870376, "title": "不用密码记录器，实在顶不住了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1021658", "created": 1709852705, "deleted": 0, "content": "工作以及生活中密码实在太多了，复杂度又高，又不能全都一样。\r\n\r\n请问一下各位，有什么比较好用的密码记录器？\r\n\r\n目前知道的就 `LastPass` 以及 `1Password`，期待各位的分享。\r\n\r\n感谢！🙏", "content_rendered": "<p>工作以及生活中密码实在太多了，复杂度又高，又不能全都一样。</p>\n<p>请问一下各位，有什么比较好用的密码记录器？</p>\n<p>目前知道的就 <code>LastPass</code> 以及 <code>1Password</code>，期待各位的分享。</p>\n<p>感谢！🙏</p>\n", "last_modified": 1709866540, "replies": 92, "id": 1021658}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6974/ce5a/103_large.png?m=1643940030", "name": "blogger", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6974/ce5a/103_normal.png?m=1643940030", "title": "Blogger", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/blogger", "topics": 258, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Blogger", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6974/ce5a/103_mini.png?m=1643940030", "stars": 126, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 103, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 561298, "username": "TArysiyehua", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/TArysiyehua", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ba193a88bd6889dcf504d38e8bca792f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ba193a88bd6889dcf504d38e8bca792f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ba193a88bd6889dcf504d38e8bca792f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1636449448, "last_modified": 1709787264}, "last_reply_by": "z09n", "last_touched": 1709835798, "title": "请教大佬们推荐博客系统?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1021421", "created": 1709787818, "deleted": 0, "content": "我想自己搭建博客系统，要求：\r\n\r\n1. 有分类，搜索功能\r\n2. 能支持代码，图片，视频\r\n3. 能增加评论（可以以 github 登录或者直接普通注册），主要是为了跟读者交流\r\n4. 能直接写 markdown 即可发表自己的文章\r\n\r\n我自己有：\r\n1. 轻量级服务器\r\n2. 会使用 vercel\r\n\r\n\r\n不想：\r\n1. 不想写前端样式或代码（主要麻烦，能用 markdown 就可以了）\r\n\r\n\r\n我看了论坛里的其他的推荐，都不太符合我的要求。主要是大部分都有评论功能，或者是要求去学一种前端语言，没有直接用 markdown 就能写的。\r\n\r\n麻烦各位大佬，彦祖们推荐，感谢！！！", "content_rendered": "<p>我想自己搭建博客系统，要求：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>有分类，搜索功能</li>\n<li>能支持代码，图片，视频</li>\n<li>能增加评论（可以以 github 登录或者直接普通注册），主要是为了跟读者交流</li>\n<li>能直接写 markdown 即可发表自己的文章</li>\n</ol>\n<p>我自己有：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>轻量级服务器</li>\n<li>会使用 vercel</li>\n</ol>\n<p>不想：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>不想写前端样式或代码（主要麻烦，能用 markdown 就可以了）</li>\n</ol>\n<p>我看了论坛里的其他的推荐，都不太符合我的要求。主要是大部分都有评论功能，或者是要求去学一种前端语言，没有直接用 markdown 就能写的。</p>\n<p>麻烦各位大佬，彦祖们推荐，感谢！！！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1709814876, "replies": 72, "id": 1021421}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1670319927", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1670319927", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 3777, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1670319927", "stars": 1206, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 602854, "username": "suqiuluck", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/suqiuluck", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a78715de6fa641ebaab6bf2a7b7167c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a78715de6fa641ebaab6bf2a7b7167c?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a78715de6fa641ebaab6bf2a7b7167c?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1669011763, "last_modified": 1701770826}, "last_reply_by": "nutting", "last_touched": 1709870290, "title": "AI 需求，主机配置推荐， 2024 年准备 all in AI", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1021687", "created": 1709861694, "deleted": 0, "content": "网上看到这套配置，值得入吗大佬们，你们都是啥配置的，显卡值得上 4090 吗？\r\nCPU：Intel 13400F\r\n主板：华硕 B660M 重炮手\r\n显卡：七彩虹战斧 RTX4060Ti 16GB\r\n内存：